{"tid":2291963,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"支大又贏","createTime":"2020-11-19T06:53:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-19T07:05:34.000Z","uid":29836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"4890a8dadb1147c7534b44da3bb603659d680c1c","tid":2291963,"uid":29836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T06:53:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n支大發表聲明：<br />\n<br />\n大學今天 （11月19日）清晨發現校園多處遭人以噴漆塗鴉，包括書院、教學樓及公共空間的多座建築物的牆壁、通道及地面，可能造成永久損壞。大學強烈讉責此等違法及不負責任行為，由於相關行為屬於刑事毀壞，大學已經報警處理。<br />\n<br />\n鑑於大型人群聚集會為校園帶來健康風險，而且相關行為很可能觸犯第599G章《預防及控制疾病（禁止羣組聚集）規例》，亦可能違反《公安條例》（第245章）就公眾集會或公眾遊行的相關規限，大學為防情況失控，已經就此通報警方。<br />\n<br />\nSource:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cpr.cuhk.edu.hk/en/announcements_detail.php?id=122&amp;t=%E4%B8%AD%E5%A4%A7%E8%81%B2%E6%98%8E-chinese-version-only&amp;s=\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cpr.cuhk.edu.hk%2Fen%2Fannouncements_detail.php%3Fid%3D122%26t%3D%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E8%2581%25B2%25E6%2598%258E-chinese-version-only%26s%3D&d=VbAd486K8RrC2DEUtq3b5uQdxvW7LhoH5lY2nOShEJQ%3D&h=d9c5a5a6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cpr.cuhk.edu.hk/en/announcements_detail.php?id=122&amp;t=%E4%B8%AD%E5%A4%A7%E8%81%B2%E6%98%8E-chinese-version-only&amp;s=</a><br />\n<br />\n#新聞"},{"pid":"1d527e897a367e7bc98437572d20a558025d09c1","tid":2291963,"uid":9392,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T06:58:52.000Z","msg":"得架喇知架喇死去po ig story拎光環啦屌你老母"},{"pid":"b15864b2ed01981f3b0e7543965a9041d9f1320e","tid":2291963,"uid":199227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T07:05:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}